---

<Layout
    title={t({
        ja: "メンバー紹介",
        en: "Our Members",
        zh: "成员介绍",
    })}
    description={t({
        ja: "OUS Metaverseのメンバーをご紹介します。代表、副代表をはじめ、多様なスキルを持ったメンバーが揃っています。",
        en: "Introducing the members of OUS Metaverse. We have members with diverse skills, including our president and vice president.",
        zh: "介绍OUS Metaverse的成员。我们有各种技能的成员，包括代表和副代表。",
    })}
>
    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#6CB16E]/20 to-white py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 md:text-5xl">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "メンバー紹介",
                            en: "Our Members",
                            zh: "成员介绍",
                        })
                    }
                </h1>
                <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-3xl text-lg text-gray-600">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "OUS Metaverseは多様なスキルと興味を持つメンバーで構成されています。一人ひとりの得意分野を活かしながら、メタバースの新たな可能性を追求しています。",
                            en: "OUS Metaverse consists of members with diverse skills and interests. While leveraging each member's strengths, we pursue new possibilities in the metaverse.",
                            zh: "OUS Metaverse由具有不同技能和兴趣的成员组成。我们在发挥每个成员的优势的同时，探索元宇宙的新可能性。",
                        })
                    }
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Staff Members Section -->
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "運営メンバー",
                            en: "Staff Members",
                            zh: "运营成员",
                        })
                    }
                </h2>

                <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
                    {
                        staffMembers.map((member) => (
                            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white shadow-lg">
                                <div class="md:flex">
                                    <div class="md:w-1/3">
                                        <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden">
                                            <img
                                                src={member.avatar}
                                                alt={member.name}
                                                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                                            />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="p-6 md:w-2/3">
                                        <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                                            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-[#6CB16E]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#6CB16E]">
                                                {t(member.role)}
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                                            {member.name}
                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="mb-3 text-sm text-gray-500">{t(member.grade)}</p>

                                        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">{t(member.comment)}</p>

                                        {member.skills && member.skills.length > 0 && (
                                            <div class="mb-4">
                                                <h4 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">
                                                    {t({
                                                        ja: "スキル・得意分野",
                                                        en: "Skills & Expertise",
                                                        zh: "技能和专长",
                                                    })}
                                                </h4>
                                                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                                                    {member.skills.map((skill) => (
                                                        <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-gray-700">
                                                            {skill}
                                                        </span>
                                                    ))}
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        )}

                                        {member.socials && member.socials.length > 0 && (
                                            <div class="flex space-x-2">
                                                {member.socials.map((social) => (
                                                    <a
                                                        href={social.url}
                                                        target="_blank"
                                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                                        class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-[#6CB16E] hover:text-white"
                                                        aria-label={social.name}
                                                    >
                                                        <Icon name={social.icon} class="h-4 w-4" />
                                                    </a>
                                                ))}
                                            </div>
                                        )}
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Regular Members Section -->
        <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "一般メンバー",
                            en: "Regular Members",
                            zh: "普通成员",
                        })
                    }
                </h2>

                <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
                    {
                        regularMembers.map((member) => (
                            <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition hover:shadow-lg">
                                <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
                                    <div class="h-24 w-24 overflow-hidden rounded-full border-4 border-[#6CB16E]/20">
                                        <img
                                            src={member.avatar}
                                            alt={member.name}
                                            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                                        />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">
                                        {member.name}
                                    </h3>
                                    <p class="mb-3 text-sm text-gray-500">{t(member.grade)}</p>

                                    {member.skills && member.skills.length > 0 && (
                                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-1">
                                            {member.skills.map((skill) => (
                                                <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-gray-700">
                                                    {skill}
                                                </span>
                                            ))}
                                        </div>
                                    )}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Join Us Section -->
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "私たちと一緒に活動しませんか？",
                            en: "Would You Like to Join Us?",
                            zh: "想与我们一起活动吗？",
                        })
                    }
                </h2>
                <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-600">
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "OUS Metaverseでは、メタバースに興味のあるメンバーを随時募集しています。プログラミング、デザイン、企画、広報など、あなたの得意分野を活かして一緒に活動しましょう！",
                            en: "OUS Metaverse is always recruiting members interested in the metaverse. Let's work together using your strengths in programming, design, planning, PR, and more!",
                            zh: "OUS Metaverse一直在招募对元宇宙感兴趣的成员。让我们一起利用您在编程、设计、规划、公关等方面的优势一起工作吧！",
                        })
                    }
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/join"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[#6CB16E] px-6 py-3 text-white transition hover:bg-[#5a9a5c]"
                >
                    {
                        t({
                            ja: "参加方法を見る",
                            en: "See How to Join",
                            zh: "查看如何加入",
                        })
                    }
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="ml-2 h-5 w-5"
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                        fill="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
